channel.title: Galaxy317 Presents: Oldschool, An Eco Version. PK/PVM | Featuring Zulrah&Kraken!
channel.description:
Hello Runescape Private Server Community :cool: I'm Galactic, I'm going to be talking about My new osrs release today.
[size=18pt]Galactic Oldschool![/size]
If you'd like to skip the BS, and play now Instantly for free, You can download the client here: [SIZE=5]www.galaxy317.com[/SIZE]
If you're having trouble loading the client, feel free to message me on [SIZE=4]SKYPE: "wwsupden"[/SIZE]
Now for the fun stuff :D
Features: Kraken boss, drops tentacle. Zulrah, drops her scales, and toxic blowpipe. Corp, Kbd, Venanatis, Vet'ion, Godwars + So much more
Abyssal Dagger! Tentacle! Toxic Blowpipe! Armadyl Crossbow! Spirit shields! Dragon Warhammer! Primordial & Pegasian Boots!
